strings.Value: "Ugh… I feel like I'm ready to drop…"
"My hide is intact, but I feel like crap…"
"I'm sorry we can't do anything for you right now. Maybe we'll find you some help in town..."
"Such a familiar feeling… wait, were you speaking of bodily suffering? For a moment I thought you meant your haggard soul."
"Don't forget to call me if you decide you're ready to die. I wouldn't want to miss a show like that!"
"Quite some stamina... for a creature so short-lived."
"Maybe ate something? Nok-Nok once ate a fish he kept in earth for a week — nearly sick to death!"
